eLayer"},{"text":" at high zoom levels. If you are unsure whether the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"point data in an ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNHeatmapStyleLayer"},{"text":" is dense enough to warrant a heatmap,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"you can alternatively cluster the source using the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNHeatmapStyleLayer"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"option and render the data using an ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNHeatmapStyleLayer"},{"text":" or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNHeatmapStyleLayer"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can access an existing heatmap style layer using the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle\/layerWithIdentifier:"},{"type":"text","text":" method if you know its identifier;"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"otherwise, find it using the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle\/layers"},{"type":"text","text":" property. You can also create a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"new heatmap style layer and add it to the style using a method such as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle\/addLayer:","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Related examples","type":"heading","level":4,"anchor":